headline: 2 Dividend Stocks to Double Up on Right Now
summary: Total return can offer insights about a company's prospects and long-term earnings growth potential.  The S&P 500 is up over 27% this year (through Dec. 6).  Two S&P 500 components, Target (NYSE: TGT) and Lowe's (NYSE: LOW), have lagged the market by varying degrees so far in 2024.
